high_descs: turn around and walk to the end of the kitchen
grab a bowl off of the counter on your right
turn around and walk to until you reach the fridge on your left
place the bowl inside of the fridge and let it cool for a bit, then take it back out
turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen counter on your left, then turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen counter on your right, and turn right to face it
place the bowl on the second brown shelf of the shelves on your left
anns.task_desc: place a cooled bowl down on the brown kitchen shelves

high_descs: Turn around and head past the sink to the counter.
Pick up the bowl on the counter next to the sink.
Turn around and bring the bowl to the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge.
Take the bowl out and back towards the sink, then make a left and bring the bowl to the wooden rack.
Put the bowl on the second shelf of the wooden rack next to the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bowl on the wooden rack.

high_descs: Face the opposite direction and go forward across the room to the counter.
Pick up the bowl to the right of the hand.
Turn back around and go forward to the fridge, then turn left to face it.
Put the bowl into the fridge next to the tomato, then take it out again.
Turn left and go counterclockwise until you come to the end of the counter, then face the baker's rack at the end of the counter.
Set the bowl on the middle shelf of the brown rack, to the left of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl on a shelf of a brown baker's rack.
